Jim Alexander:
 That's a separate issue.

00:06:53.149 --> 00:06:58.959
Anyway--so I was--one of my
past clients,

00:06:58.959 --> 00:07:00.911
and I was there,
actually, at the start of

00:07:00.911 --> 00:07:03.293
Enron,
because I was there--we helped

